575
00:28:17.983 --> 00:28:20.644
Oh.
Uh. new guitar.

576
00:28:20.646 --> 00:28:22.200
Check it out.

577
00:28:24.861 --> 00:28:26.848
Mm.
That is something.

578
00:28:27.379 --> 00:28:29.157
