I can call.
Need to reschedule?

642
00:31:22.665 --> 00:31:24.236
No. cancel it.

643
00:31:24.284 --> 00:31:26.439
And get Billy Gatwood
on the phone for me.

644
00:31:26.566 --> 00:31:28.728
- Will do.
- Thanks.

645
