662
00:32:07.885 --> 00:32:10.019
Figured I'd wait. in case...

663
00:32:10.259 --> 00:32:12.173
- Are those groceries?
- They are.

664
00:32:12.673 --> 00:32:14.665
I decided
to go for a little walk.

665
00:32:15.026 --> 00:32:17.027
That's great. chuck. [Chuckles]
why don't you come on in?

666
00:32:17.074 --> 00:32:18.907
Uh. thank you.

667
00:32:19.774 --> 00:32:21.218
