668
00:32:21.345 --> 00:32:23.321
Well. I wish it was just
a social call.

669
00:32:23.369 --> 00:32:26.001
but unfortunately. we do have
an issue we need to discuss.

670
00:32:26.141 --> 00:32:27.219
What's that?

671
00:32:27.415 --> 00:32:29.581
