your malpractice insurance.

672
00:32:29.849 --> 00:32:31.182
There's...

673
00:32:32.125 --> 00:32:35.723
Well. we should sit
and talk it through.

674
00:32:38.731 --> 00:32:40.395
[Horn honks in distance]

675
00:32:40.443 --> 00:32:42.338
[Vehicles passing in distance]

676
00:32:44.709 --> 00:32:47.010
