698
00:35:27.385 --> 00:35:29.000
You see?
Is it fake?

699
00:35:33.943 --> 00:35:36.153
No. it's fine.

700
00:35:41.116 --> 00:35:43.104
I'm so sorry. Don Hector.

701
00:35:43.243 --> 00:35:44.483
[Money thumps]

702
00:35:51.246 --> 00:35:55.176
[Music continues]

703
00:36:11.296 --> 00:36:14.366
[Money rustling]

704
00:36:21.494 --> 00:36:23.455
[Sniffles]

705
00:36:33.288 --> 00:36:35.688
[Los panchos'
<i>"hasta mañana"</i> plays]

706
00:36:36.287 --> 00:36:37.361
[Sniffles]

707
00:36:37.633 --> 00:36:38.849
[Door creaks]

708
00:36:40.154 --> 00:36:41.184
Carlos.

709
00:36:41.232 --> 00:36:42.798
Nacho.

710
00:36:53.042 --> 00:36:54.417
I'm heavy.

711
00:36:54.746 --> 00:36:56.862
Took care of that problem
over on fifth.

712
00:36:57.300 --> 00:36:58.768
That crew
won't bother us no more...

713
00:36:58.835 --> 00:37:01.448
- Hey. do me a favor.
- Shut up.

714
00:37:06.907 --> 00:37:08.454
You're good.

715
00:37:08.843 --> 00:37:09.931
Okay.

716
00:37:12.114 --> 00:37:14.439
See you next week.

717
00:37:22.876 --> 00:37:24.771
[Door opens]

718
00:37:26.724 --> 00:37:28.635
[Door closes]

719
00:37:46.395 --> 00:37:47.995
[pills rattling softly]

720
00:38:28.485 --> 00:38:30.403
[sniffles]

721
