730
00:39:58.034 --> 00:39:59.315
Man: Mcgill.

731
00:39:59.648 --> 00:40:01.921
Keep it moving.

732
00:40:05.029 --> 00:40:08.005
[Wind whistling]

733
00:40:08.470 --> 00:40:10.500
[Groans]

734
00:40:11.443 --> 00:40:12.551
Freddy: Sir. Sir.

735
00:40:12.599 --> 00:40:13.716
What's up?

736
00:40:13.786 --> 00:40:16.916
Hey. uh.
it's... it's my kid.

737
00:40:17.006 --> 00:40:18.022
Her mom just called.

738
00:40:18.087 --> 00:40:20.115
You're not
supposed to be on the phone.

739
00:40:20.235 --> 00:40:21.320
I know. I know. but she's sick.

740
00:40:21.367 --> 00:40:22.818
She caught pneumonia
at day care.

741
00:40:22.873 --> 00:40:23.896
She's in the hospital.

742
00:40:23.944 --> 00:40:25.787
- Please. can I go?
- Sure. you can go.

743
00:40:25.835 --> 00:40:27.137
But you're not gettin' credit.

744
00:40:27.185 --> 00:40:29.155
C'mon. can I just go
and come right back?

745
00:40:29.623 --> 00:40:31.623
I have to get my hours done
this week.

746
00:40:31.908 --> 00:40:32.998
Judge says so.

747
00:40:33.046 --> 00:40:34.679
Judge told you. huh?

748
00:40:34.913 --> 00:40:36.913
Sounds like that's on you.

749
00:40:49.544 --> 00:40:51.070
[Freddy scoffs]

750
00:40:51.071 --> 00:40:52.533
Hey. buddy.
you wanna get outta here?

751
00:40:52.581 --> 00:40:53.744
How much is it worth to you?

752
00:40:53.792 --> 00:40:54.955
What?

753
00:40:56.103 --> 00:40:57.150
To ditch this.

754
00:40:57.260 --> 00:40:59.494
- How much?
- Leave me alone. yo.

755
00:41:00.048 --> 00:41:01.129
Come on.

756
00:41:01.192 --> 00:41:03.009
You want to get
to your deal or what?

757
00:41:03.402 --> 00:41:06.001
Man. I was just tryin'
ta see my sick kid.

758
00:41:06.464 --> 00:41:08.579
You're trying to sell
something you shouldn't have

759
00:41:08.627 --> 00:41:10.369
to someone
who shouldn't be buying it.

760
00:41:11.806 --> 00:41:13.353
Hey.
No judgments. all right?

761
00:41:13.408 --> 00:41:14.462
Man's gotta make a living.

762
00:41:14.510 --> 00:41:16.954
I'm just saying
the way you make yours

763
00:41:17.054 --> 00:41:18.853
Rhymes with
"Mug Mealer."

764
00:41:18.944 --> 00:41:20.548
- Yeah.
- What are you... a Narc?

765
00:41:20.596 --> 00:41:22.296
I'm the guy
who's gonna get you out of here

766
00:41:22.344 --> 00:41:24.522
- And let you keep your hours.
- Yeah?

767
00:41:24.602 --> 00:41:26.170
- Yeah.
- How you gonna do that?

768
00:41:26.235 --> 00:41:28.319
Lemme worry about the how. okay?

769
00:41:28.395 --> 00:41:29.828
You just...

770
00:41:30.268 --> 00:41:32.256
700 bucks. and you're gone.

771
00:41:32.569 --> 00:41:34.866
No. I don't have 700 bucks.

772
00:41:35.181 --> 00:41:38.515
Hey. you got a couple grand
in your sock.

773
00:41:44.466 --> 00:41:46.266
[Scoffs]

774
00:41:46.268 --> 00:41:47.728
[Sniffles]

775
00:41:41.846 --> 00:41:43.135
700 bucks.

776
00:41:43.183 --> 00:41:44.690
And you can get me outta here?

777
00:41:46.921 --> 00:41:47.940
[Scoffs] Aight.

778
00:41:48.117 --> 00:41:50.000
You can do it. you got a deal.

779
00:41:51.218 --> 00:41:52.296
Okay.

780
00:41:52.414 --> 00:41:54.847
Just go pick up trash.
Go on.

781
00:42:00.616 --> 00:42:02.776
[Creaking]

782
00:42:07.188 --> 00:42:09.045
[Sighs]

783
00:42:09.537 --> 00:42:12.287
[Footsteps approach]

784
00:42:12.526 --> 00:42:14.721
The hell's this?

785
00:42:16.398 --> 00:42:19.299
Resting.
Uh. hurt my back.

786
00:42:19.607 --> 00:42:20.783
Get up.

787
00:42:20.975 --> 00:42:23.557
Nope.
My back's killing me.

788
00:42:23.627 --> 00:42:24.993
Suit yourself.

789
00:42:25.331 --> 00:42:26.994
You're not getting your hours.

790
00:42:27.042 --> 00:42:29.713
I'm pretty sure you're gonna
give me my hours.

791
00:42:29.867 --> 00:42:31.096
Oh. yeah?

792
00:42:31.697 --> 00:42:33.221
And how do you figure that?

793
00:42:33.341 --> 00:42:35.830
'cause if you don't.
I'm gonna sue you.

794
00:42:35.878 --> 00:42:36.800
[Chuckles]

795
00:42:36.848 --> 00:42:39.213
Hate to break it to you.
smart guy.

796
00:42:39.261 --> 00:42:41.194
But you signed a waiver.

797
00:42:41.292 --> 00:42:43.135
I signed a waiver with the city.

798
00:42:43.197 --> 00:42:44.877
But I'm not suing the<i> city.</i>

799
00:42:44.945 --> 00:42:47.729
I'm suing<i> you!</i>
Personally!

800
00:42:50.556 --> 00:42:52.096
You can't do that.

801
00:42:52.916 --> 00:42:54.140
Buddy...

802
00:42:54.544 --> 00:42:56.490
[Groans]

803
00:42:56.788 --> 00:42:59.757
This is the land of the free
and the home of the lawsuit...

804
00:42:59.805 --> 00:43:01.404
I sure as shootin' can.

805
00:43:01.611 --> 00:43:02.734
And you know what?

806
00:43:02.887 --> 00:43:06.116
I think I'll bring that guy
in with me

807
00:43:06.189 --> 00:43:08.296
And make it
a class-action thing.

808
00:43:08.613 --> 00:43:09.835
What's he got to do with it?

809
00:43:09.884 --> 00:43:12.390
You knowingly prevented him
from visiting his child

810
00:43:12.438 --> 00:43:13.523
in the hospital.

811
00:43:13.571 --> 00:43:15.273
If that isn't
intentional infliction

812
00:43:15.320 --> 00:43:17.265
of emotional distress. what is?

813
00:43:17.923 --> 00:43:19.710
That's... Crazy.

814
00:43:19.758 --> 00:43:21.235
[Chuckling]
Crazy hasn't even started.

815
00:43:21.282 --> 00:43:22.351
I can also sue you

816
00:43:22.399 --> 00:43:24.663
for failure to approve
community-service hours...

817
00:43:24.726 --> 00:43:27.274
That's a direct violation
of your duties

818
00:43:27.431 --> 00:43:29.351
as an Agent
of the State of New Mexico.

819
00:43:29.453 --> 00:43:30.919
I'm only doin' my job...

820
00:43:30.967 --> 00:43:33.359
and just for tickles.
maybe I throw in

821
00:43:33.407 --> 00:43:35.812
Failure to treat
and mitigate damages

822
00:43:35.893 --> 00:43:36.976
suffered by me

823
00:43:37.051 --> 00:43:39.171
due to injuries
sustained under your watch.

824
00:43:39.219 --> 00:43:40.652
- Injury?
- My back.

825
00:43:40.789 --> 00:43:43.226
You're full of shit.
The waiver clearly states...

826
00:43:43.274 --> 00:43:44.186
[chuckling] Now. that waiver's

827
00:43:44.234 --> 00:43:46.718
gonna make swiss cheese
look solid.

828
00:43:47.017 --> 00:43:50.226
And in a personal lawsuit.
it's a fart in the wind.

829
00:43:52.191 --> 00:43:54.274
You're never gonna win that.

830
00:43:54.721 --> 00:43:56.388
Maybe.
Maybe not.

831
00:43:56.641 --> 00:43:58.930
In order to find out.
we gotta do some math.

832
00:43:58.978 --> 00:43:59.938
let's see.

833
00:44:00.002 --> 00:44:01.892
A lawyer's gonna cost you
about 90 bucks an hour.

834
00:44:01.939 --> 00:44:05.359
You're looking at 8 to 12 months
of litigation. minimum.

835
00:44:06.609 --> 00:44:07.805
I'll represent myself.

836
00:44:07.853 --> 00:44:09.297
[Chuckling] Great!
Bring it on.

837
00:44:09.362 --> 00:44:11.008
You got a car?
You got a house?

838
00:44:11.139 --> 00:44:13.383
A pension?
Kiss it all goodbye.

839
00:44:13.479 --> 00:44:16.875
Look. out here.
you might be King Douche-nozzle.

840
00:44:16.937 --> 00:44:20.695
But in court.
you are little people.

841
00:44:20.967 --> 00:44:22.219
Look. the judge and I...

842
00:44:22.267 --> 00:44:24.859
we'll gladly spend the next
five years in the courtroom.

843
00:44:24.973 --> 00:44:26.258
But for you. it's expensive.

844
00:44:26.306 --> 00:44:28.133
It's very. very expensive.

845
00:44:28.189 --> 00:44:30.508
It's...
third-mortgage expensive.

846
00:44:30.560 --> 00:44:34.524
So... I'm offering you
a simple choice.

847
00:44:34.719 --> 00:44:35.805
You can go to your wife.

848
00:44:35.853 --> 00:44:37.853
You can explain to her
you're about to lose your job.

849
00:44:37.900 --> 00:44:41.168
your pension. and whatever
pinhole of a reputation

850
00:44:41.221 --> 00:44:44.655
you've got at the Bowling Alley
on Glow-Ball Sundays.

851
00:44:44.775 --> 00:44:47.039
or let my friend here
visit his sick daughter

852
00:44:47.087 --> 00:44:48.110
in the hospital.

853
00:44:48.158 --> 00:44:49.594
And you can let me rest my back

854
00:44:49.642 --> 00:44:54.045
on this sacred.
now litter-free New Mexico Soil.

855
00:44:54.155 --> 00:44:56.922
Oh. and we keep our hours.

856
00:44:57.031 --> 00:45:00.232
[Wind rushing]

857
00:45:00.567 --> 00:45:03.624
[Vehicles passing]

858
00:45:03.912 --> 00:45:05.537
Fine.

859
00:45:06.701 --> 00:45:08.990
Asshole.

860
00:45:12.725 --> 00:45:14.296
Well. go on!

861
00:45:15.008 --> 00:45:16.452
Get outta here.

862
00:45:16.518 --> 00:45:17.818
[Chuckles]

863
00:45:18.490 --> 00:45:19.789
Hey. man.

864
00:45:20.236 --> 00:45:23.738
That was some
Jedi mind shit right there!

865
00:45:23.858 --> 00:45:26.118
[Chuckles]

866
00:45:26.166 --> 00:45:28.421
[Wind rushing]

867
00:45:28.709 --> 00:45:32.162
The best $700 I done ever spent.

868
00:45:36.857 --> 00:45:38.139
Here you go.

869
00:45:38.202 --> 00:45:40.045
I'm out.

870
00:45:40.708 --> 00:45:43.738
[Cellphone dialing]

871
00:45:44.330 --> 00:45:45.563
Yeah. yeah.

872
00:45:45.940 --> 00:45:48.407
Yo. I'm on my way.
Yeah. yeah.

873
00:45:48.516 --> 00:45:53.601
[Wind rushing]

874
00:45:55.277 --> 00:45:56.710
[Sighs]

875
00:46:07.511 --> 00:46:11.179
♪♪

876
00:46:15.984 --> 00:46:19.828
♪♪

877
00:46:20.018 --> 00:46:21.398
[sighs]

878
00:46:28.183 --> 00:46:36.183
♪♪

879
00:46:36.291 --> 00:46:39.761
[insects chirping]

880
00:46:39.861 --> 00:46:42.731
♪♪

881
00:46:42.782 --> 00:46:44.552
♪♪

882
00:46:44.746 --> 00:46:46.514
[keys jingling]

883
00:46:46.607 --> 00:46:49.537
♪♪

884
00:46:49.654 --> 00:46:52.342
Mike: I've got a problem
I think you can help me with.

885
00:46:52.475 --> 00:46:54.748
I've got cash I can't spend.

886
00:46:55.507 --> 00:46:57.920
About $200.000.

887
00:46:58.998 --> 00:47:00.521
If anything happens to me.

888
00:47:00.626 --> 00:47:02.935
my family'll never see it.

889
00:47:04.677 --> 00:47:08.013
Now. it seems to me
you opened this place

890
00:47:08.061 --> 00:47:10.560
to solve a similar problem.

891
00:47:11.896 --> 00:47:16.592
And you think that solution
could be applied to you.

892
00:47:16.819 --> 00:47:18.853
as a
one-time arrangement.

893
00:47:21.513 --> 00:47:24.490
It would be unwise for us
to be publicly associated.

894
00:47:24.634 --> 00:47:25.954
wouldn't you agree?

895
00:47:27.469 --> 00:47:29.123
Because of the Salamancas.

896
00:47:29.171 --> 00:47:31.271
If they were to take notice.

897
00:47:31.505 --> 00:47:35.404
there would be consequences
for both of us.

898
00:47:39.355 --> 00:47:41.589
I'm thinking
a paper transaction.

899
00:47:42.175 --> 00:47:44.066
Even so.

900
00:47:47.042 --> 00:47:49.289
Perhaps there is a way.

901
00:47:49.777 --> 00:47:52.339
One with a degree more...

902
00:47:52.492 --> 00:47:53.863
difficulty.

903
00:47:54.379 --> 00:47:56.831
But one I may be able
to arrange.

904
00:47:58.549 --> 00:48:02.089
Would 20%
overcome this difficulty?

905
00:48:03.714 --> 00:48:06.214
I would not take money
from your family

906
00:48:06.518 --> 00:48:10.388
[Clock ticking]

907
00:48:10.952 --> 00:48:14.327
[Chair scrapes]

